      "date": "2012-05-13 21:36:59.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.8/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/fc592ca8-9d40-11e1-8587-52540035b04c).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
